PHP
debug_print_backtrace()
Function
PHP Error Reference
Example
Print a PHP backtrace:
<?php
function a($txt) {
b("Glenn");
}
function b($txt) {
c("Cleveland");
}
function c($txt) {
debug_print_backtrace();
}
a("Peter");
?>

